- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of the Kronecker form and reduction of bilinear forms, which are techniques used in linear algebra and can be applied in machine learning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper discusses the reduction of bilinear forms over a non-commutative algebra, which is a topic in control theory.
